menu "BirdNET detector"

config BIRDNET_WIFI_SSID
    string "WiFi SSID (for NTP time sync)"
    default ""
    help
        Name of the WiFi network the device joins to fetch the current date/time
        over SNTP. The time drives the seasonal occurrence prior (which birds are
        likely during the current week at the configured location). Leave blank
        to skip WiFi entirely; the seasonal prior then stays disabled.

config BIRDNET_WIFI_PASSWORD
    string "WiFi password"
    default ""
    help
        Password for BIRDNET_WIFI_SSID. This is saved only in sdkconfig, which is
        gitignored in this project, so it is never committed.

endmenu
